  .information-body
    p
      | The Solomon R. Guggenheim Foundation (the “Guggenheim”) provides #[a(href="mailto:azone.guggenheim.org") azone@guggenheim.org] and its related services, including RSS feeds, mobile websites and mobile applications (such services, collectively, referred to herein as the “Site”), in support of its charitable and educational mission to collect, preserve, and interpret modern and contemporary art, and explore ideas across cultures through dynamic curatorial and educational initiatives and collaborations.  With its constellation of architecturally and culturally distinct museums, exhibitions, publications, and digital platforms, the Guggenheim engages both local and global audiences.  We encourage you to use the Site as a research and information tool, subject to the specific terms and conditions of use (the “Terms and Conditions of Use”) set forth below.
